room_title: Escape room "T-Rex Lockdown" by Exit 4 Private Escape Rooms in Collingswood
room_description: During a preview tour of a park stocked with ferocious dinosaurs, the power goes out and the predators break free. Your only chance at survival is to seek refuge in a remote dinosaur pen and find a way to restore power to the electric fence to keep the nearby T-Rex at bay!
